===Etymology===
From [[w:Rudolf Mössbauer|Rudolf Mössbauer]] German phycisist
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[Mössbauer]] [[effect]]'''
#{{physics}} the [[resonant]] and [[recoil]]-[[free]] [[emission]] and [[absorption]] of [[gamma ray]]s by [[atom]]s in the solid state; the basis of a type of [[spectroscopy]] with applications in both [[physics]] and [[chemistry]]

====Synonyms====
*[[nuclear gamma resonance fluorescence]]

